<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1912,2009]" pageId="3" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,285,1912,1937]" pageId="3" pageNumber="39">Colour.</emphasis>
Body light yellowish brown (probably green alive, or yellowish brown). Lateral margins of pronotum with yellowish white longitudinal stripes. Eyes yellowish brown. Apices of spines of posttibiae yellowish brown. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,291,1985,2009]" pageId="3" pageNumber="39">Female.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
